    "For the Ae.",
    "tauschii accessions, 'high molecular weight' genomic DNA was isolated from leaf tissue of three to four-week-old dark-treated seedlings.",
    "We followed the high molecular weight DNA isolation protocol optimized by Driguez et al.",
    "49 for long-read sequencing.",
    "DNA integrity was confirmed using the FemtoPulse system (Agilent)."
